Carlotta Monterey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlotta_Monterey 0 Carlotta Monterey (born Hazel Neilson Taasinge; December 28, 1888 – November 18, 1970) was an American stage and film actress. She was the third and final wife of playwright Eugene O'Neill. Carlotta_Monterey ( born Hazel_Neilson_Taasinge ; December_28_,_1888 – November_18_,_1970 ) was an_American_stage_and_film_actress .
